"DD","1","Re-assessed","Records of this genus are sporadic and tend to follow the activity of individual recorders / identifiers rather than any true distribution. Details of biology and ecology are imperfectly known.","No","0"
"DD","2","Maintained","Records of this genus are sporadic and tend to follow the activity of individual recorders / identifiers rather than any true distribution. Details of biology and ecology are imperfectly known.","No","0"
