"LC","68","Maintained","Whilst the distribution on the map changes, the overall number of cells remains relatively consistent throughout. Multiple metrics suggest that any changes in spread are due to a lack of detection rather than true changes in distribution.","No","2"
"LC","69","Maintained","","No","0"
"LC","70","Maintained","","No","0"
"NT","71","Maintained","Evidence suggests that the host plant is decreasing, even as far north as Cumbria. Whilst the taxon is currently common where it is found, this is projected to change within the projected 100 year time period used under A3.","No","2"
