"VU","474","Maintained","This taxon was reviewed considerably by the core team, with the final decision being taken to maintain the status of VU based on A2 Expert Inference. Mike Edwards specifically reiterated that active, reproducing nests have declined by at least 30% over the past decade, to the best of his knowledge. It was also pointed out that large nest mounds are the sign of a struggling nest, not of success.","No","0"
