"NT","522","Maintained","Further analysis of the data, including that from iRecord, shows a very distinct lack of records from south of the Wash-Severn line. This variation is far past the point where it could be considered a year-on-year fluctuation.","No","2"
"LC","523","Maintained","","No","0"
"NT","524","Maintained","Multiple sources have noted this to have declined over large areas. The decline is less than that of D. sylvestris, but iRecord data also reflects a lower volume of data in the area south of the Severn-Wash line.","No","2"
