"NT","578","Maintained","Reviewers match the A2 Expert Inference of LC, but the status of NT is based on the status of the saltmarsh habitat and coastal squeeze over a 100 year period. This aspect is picked up by one reviewer, who wishes to elevate the status based on this fact. As a compromise, the status of NT has been maintained.","No","3"
