"LC","614","Maintained","The data supports the idea that variation in records is primarily driven by the activity of recorders rather than true presence.","No","2"
"LC","615","Maintained","Species is maintaining its range and occupancy, even if restricted. London presence is predominantly on the commons, which have not been sampled recently within the data available.","No","2"
